Exploitation


Using the credentials above, I was able to gain access to SSH as skyfuck.

Privilege Escalation


The host contains two files: credential.pgp and tryhackme.asc.


The PGP file is interesting. I used gpg2john to obtain the hash of this file. Then I was able to crack it using john. The credential I received is alexandru:tryhackme.


Then I decrypted the gpg file. First the key was decrypted using the passphrase alexandru. We did receive another credential after all this: merlin:asuyusdoiuqoilkda312j31k2j123j1g23g12k3g12kj3gk12jg3k12j3kj123j. Trying this credentials did not work for SSH. Maybe we can login as skyfuck first and then switch user to merlin with the new password?


And this worked! Now I am merlin!
